US.COMMENTAIRE:
Three possible meanings:
1) The farmers come to check their paddy fields to monitor the rice growth, just as barren women are visited; 
2) Another informant explains that this couple shares little, like barren women who are reputed to be stingy; 
3) If everybody get small pieces, she will be considered a childless woman, because if she has no child, she can afford to be a social person.
